In general, too much patient care
in the U.S. is provided this way.

2
00:00:05,150 --> 00:00:08,882
In part, as we just discussed,
this is because of patient choice.

3
00:00:08,882 --> 00:00:15,183
But, if all patients wanted a PCP, we
don't have enough of them to go around.

4
