they leave medical school
with the same debt level.

14
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:02,110
So it shouldn't be a surprise,
as shown here, that over the years

15
00:01:02,110 --> 00:01:06,200
the percentage of medical school
graduates selecting primary care,

16
